{"tid":1815391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"if we burn you burn with us!!! 澳洲山火只係第一步","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T03:23:44.000Z","uid":68084,"like":2,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"63dfa41d6d23e762497289b694f622b151091a2b","tid":1815391,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:57:40.000Z","msg":"我正式同全世界講<br />\n<br />\n如果你地唔幫助香港脫離communist party<br />\n<br />\n下一次就唔會係山火咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n由7月開始已經通知曬全世界<br />\n<br />\n反送中不只是香港的問題<br />\n<br />\nIf we burn You burn with us!!! <br />\n<br />\nIt will be more than australia<br />\n<br />\n其他國家再唔插手香港事務<br />\n<br />\n下一個burn就係你地!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac5891b109fc8d3368de88cc75ae0f398114817","tid":1815391,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:58:51.000Z","msg":"再次重申<br />\n<br />\n反送中不只是香港問題<br />\n<br />\n所有國家如果唔幫手<br />\n<br />\n就會成為下一個澳洲"},{"pid":"3917f6a4aaeafa5ddba748c854857fc491d590c5","tid":1815391,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"呢一個係最後通碟<br />\n<br />\n如果最終不能光復香港<br />\n<br />\n保証會發生全球性人道生態災難"},{"pid":"4471c856b2106cb0d4bd5917a8730215ca37f4ce","tid":1815391,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"所以話<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n<br />\n人人有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無分國籍"},{"pid":"b957073d43d2750d0d07e82acffd92d54b9e726e","tid":1815391,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0519d0c7f44ed91d6c41d545259b2e708453dc35","tid":1815391,"uid":68084,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n垃圾英國"},{"pid":"7a9d44e1e928c91d9c0edd0a11bc64e8169d7a72","tid":181